" pointer="0" path="/webmd/consumer_assets/editorial/articles/image_collections/anatomy_pages/picture_of_the_spleen.wxml"><target siteid="3" name="WebMD" prefix="www" friendlyurl="/digestive-disorders/picture-of-the-spleen"></target><target siteid="8" name="WebMD_Mobile" prefix="www" friendlyurl="/a-to-z-guides/picture-of-the-spleen"></target></object><object chronic_id="091e9c5e804d6f9a" thmbnl="" pointer="0" path="/webmd/consumer_assets/editorial/articles/health_and_medical_reference/cancer/miscellaneous/what_to_expect_from_radiation_therapy.wxml"><target siteid="3" name="WebMD" prefix="www" friendlyurl="/cancer/what-to-expect-from-radiation-therapy"></target><target siteid="8" name="WebMD_Mobile" prefix="www" friendlyurl="/a-to-z-guides/what-to-expect-from-radiation-therapy"></target></object></referenced_objects><container_hierarchy></container_hierarchy><expanded_objects></expanded_objects><dynamic_objects><callout_title>Recommended Related to Cancer</callout_title><wbmd_asset object_type="wbmd_cons_article" id="091e9c5e80e687fc"><metadata_section><i_chronicle_id>091e9c5e807f0a67</i_chronicle_id><title>About This PDQ Summary</title><wbmd_c_art_thmbnl></wbmd_c_art_thmbnl></metadata_section><section_text><p>
  Purpose of This Summary

This PDQ cancer information summary for health professionals provides comprehensive, peer-reviewed, evidence-based information about the treatment of Wilms tumor and other childhood kidney tumors. It is intended as a resource to inform and assist clinicians who care for cancer patients. It does not provide formal guidelines or recommendations for making health care decisions.

  Reviewers and Updates

This summary is reviewed regularly and updated as necessary by...</p></section_text><link siteid="3" prefix="www" friendlyurl="/cancer/tc/ncicdr0000062789-about-this-pdq-summary"></wbmd_asset></dynamic_objects></webmd_rendition>
